# 🤖 ResumeAI – Resume Analyzer + Interview Simulator

A full-stack AI-powered web application that analyzes resumes and simulates job interviews with instant feedback.

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 [Try ResumeAI Live](https://ai-resume-interview-app.onrender.com/)

## ✨ Features

* Resume PDF Upload
* Resume Analysis
* Skill Extraction
* Job Role Matching
* Interview Simulation
* Instant Feedback
* Responsive User Interface

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

### Frontend

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* Three.js

### Backend

* Python
* Flask

### Deployment

* Render

